Package edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExecutionController
    The execution controller is a stateless controller that manages the executions of different processes, queries, and joins by creating an execution plan and running it.
    JoinController
    A stateless controller for creating and running joins.
    PathController
    A stateless controller that manages the relationships, and paths for a resource
    ProcessController
    A stateless controller for creating a process
    QueryController
    A stateless controller for creating a query
    ResourceController
    A stateless controller that provides access to all resources in the IRCT Application
    ResultController
    A stateless controller for retrieving the status of a result as well as the result themselves.
    SecurityController
    A stateless controller for managing security.
